# Force HTTPS (apex + www)
http://redplanettribe.org/*      https://redplanettribe.org/:splat 301!
http://www.redplanettribe.org/*  https://redplanettribe.org/:splat 301!

# Canonicalize host: www -> apex
https://www.redplanettribe.org/* https://redplanettribe.org/:splat 301!
